public abstract class HTMLBuilder<T extends HTMLBuilder<T>>
extends net.sf.derquinsej.This<T>
implements HTMLFragment

Abstract class for programmatic HTML fragment building. This class and its subclasses are mutable and not THREAD-SAFE.

Author:
Andres Rodriguez
